    "title": "Manufacturing Engineer - Nestle India - Top MNC",
    "description": "Nestle India has an exciting opening for a Manufacturing Engineer at our Gwalior office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Nestle India:\nNestle India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Prepare production cost analysis and efficiency reports\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Six Sigma\n• Proficiency in FMEA\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in 5S\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in TPM\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Learning & development budget\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Nestle India!",
